---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-ink/10 mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display font-extrabold text-lg text-ink lowercase tracking-tight">dumb gtm</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate mt-1">GTM advice that isn't trying to sell you a retainer.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:items-end gap-1 text-sm">
      <a href="/contact" class="text-ink/70 hover:text-siren">Get in touch</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="text-ink/70 hover:text-siren">Read the blog</a>
      <p class="text-slate">&copy; {year} dumbGTM. All rights reserved (mostly for legal reasons, not ego).</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
